profile_summary:
Shaheem PP is a highly skilled software developer with a proven track record of driving innovation and delivering high-quality technology solutions. With a strong foundation in programming languages such as Swift, C, and Python, he has built a reputation for developing robust, scalable, and reliable applications that cater to the needs of diverse industries. His expertise inSwift and SwiftUI make him a go-to developer for iOS app development, while his proficiency in Python and Django enable him to build complex web applications with ease.

As a forward-thinking developer with a passion for building web applications for social good, Shaheem has established himself as a credible and influential voice in the developer community. With 81 public repositories and a following of 46, he has demonstrated his commitment to open-source development and collaboration. His unique blend of technical expertise, creativity, and dedication to social impact make him an invaluable asset to any project or organization that seeks to harness the power of technology for positive change.
